<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1436,1822,2035]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,368,1898,1923]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Identification.</emphasis>
Test moderately sized, creamish in color. Spines white, banded brown and greenish, equatorial spines long, facing downwards, creating a fringe appearance; eccentric anal opening.
</paragraph>
